<plot>Gladys and Sadie are finally back from their trip to Europe. Gladys meets Mike, a young but superstitious prizefighter who won't fight in his upcoming bout because it will be his 13th one. Since Jerry is his manager and Jimmy is his trainer, Gladys decides to try to help him get past his superstition and fight in the match.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?200122</url></doc>
